INSERT INTO "Pages" VALUES (38, 'Family Holidays', 'http://www.destinationnsw.com.au/smartphoneapps/central-coast/things-to-do/family-holidays', 1390517653000, '44,45,46', '{"Page":{"Title":"Family Holidays","Images":[{"Full Size":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com.au\/__data\/assets\/image\/0019\/216604\/crackneck-point-lookout.jpg","Thumb":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com\/__data\/assets\/image\/0019\/216604\/varieties\/thumb.jpg","Alt":"Crackneck Point Lookout","Modified":"2013-10-02 14:43:52"},{"Full Size":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com.au\/__data\/assets\/image\/0011\/245783\/1386736.jpg","Thumb":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com\/__data\/assets\/image\/0011\/245783\/varieties\/thumb.jpg","Alt":"Family horseriding at Glenworth Valley","Modified":"2014-01-14 15:21:06"},{"Full Size":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com.au\/__data\/assets\/image\/0019\/246061\/1340556.jpg","Thumb":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com\/__data\/assets\/image\/0019\/246061\/varieties\/thumb.jpg","Alt":"Family fishing at sunrise at The Entrance","Modified":"2014-01-15 10:50:52"}],"Content":"\r\n<div id=\"content_div_215659\">\r\n<p>There is never a shortage of activities to keep the kids busy on a trip to the Central Coast! Get up close with your favourite Aussie animal at the Australian Reptile Park or head to the trees at the Treetop Adventure Park. Learn more about your favourite sea creatures at the Central Coast Marine Discovery Centre, or enjoy Pelican Feeding at The Entrance. Take the kids to get lost in the labyrinth at Amazement! A fun day out for all the family, Amazement has mazes, a games courtyard, sandpits, a wild wood walk, and cute and cuddly animals in Bunny World.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>With beautiful scenery and activities aplenty, the area is the perfect place for a camping or caravanning holiday. The Central Coast is made up of six distinct regions, each of which has its own personality, character and unique drawcard. Get the kids out into the great outdoors by visiting Glenworth Valley Outdoor Adventures or head up to the Yarramalong Valley, and get lost in the maze at Amazement, or swing through the trees at the Treetop Adventure Park.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<\/div>\r\n"},"Children":[{"Name":"Must Do Links","Url":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com.au\/smartphoneapps\/central-coast\/things-to-do\/family-holidays\/must-do-links"},{"Name":"Don\u2019t Miss","Url":"http:\/\/www.destinationnsw.com.au\/smartphoneapps\/central-coast\/things-to-do\/family-holidays\/dont-miss"}]}');
